  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为工业物联网场景设计一个TCP包结构图，重点是展示PLC逻辑层和执行器控制器的负载分布。我想把Options字段留给PLC逻辑，Data字段给执行器控制器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Options",
        "Data",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，那标准TCP头部的前160位保持原样吗？包括Source Port、Destination Port、Sequence Number这些字段？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Source Port",
        "Destination Port",
        "Sequence Number",
        "Acknowledgment Number"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，标准头部保留。但注意控制位区域要清晰标出URG、ACK、PSH、RST、SYN、FIN这六个标志位，每个占1位。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "URG",
        "ACK",
        "PSH",
        "RST",
        "SYN",
        "FIN",
        "Data Offset",
        "Reserved"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把0-15位设为Source Port，16-31位是Destination Port，控制位从106位开始依次排列。Window字段放在112-127位，Checksum和Urgent Pointer紧随其后。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Source Port",
        "Destination Port",
        "Window",
        "Checksum",
        "Urgent Pointer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Options字段的位数确认一下，160-191位对吗？32位应该够PLC逻辑用了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Options",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，160-191位共32位给Options (IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic)。那Data字段从192位开始到255位，64位给IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController，这样总长度256位。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Data",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "Options"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后加个小细节，图标题用\"Estructura del paquete TCP\"，因为我们这边有西班牙语区的合作伙伴需要看。",
      "elements_involved": [
